headline: Deutsche Bank upgrades HPE on networking growth from Juniper, valuation
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank upgraded Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co (NYSE:HPE) to "buy," given its attractive valuation and potential gains from its proposed acquisition of Juniper Networks (NYSE:JNPR). The brokerage has a price target of $25 on the stock.
